<% @body_id = 'about' %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="about-us py-5" id="about-us">
    <!-- First ABOUT US SECTION -->
    <div class="about-LFN row">
      <div class="about-LFN-image col-10 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
        <img class="lazyload"
            data-src="<%= asset_path('nails_pink.jpg') %>"
            alt="Pink Nails"/>
      </div>
      <div class="about-LFN-text col-11 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
        <h2>About LondonFineNails</h2>
        <p>
          FineNailsLondon steht für langanhaltende, zeitsparende und verlässliche Nagelpflege- ohne Kompromisse.
          Das Unternehmen wurde 2020 in London, Großbritannien, gegründet. Mit dem Ziel Individualität in der Nagelpflege anzuerkennen, verbinden wir effiziente Maniküre-Produkte mit exzellentem Service. Mit den innovativen Produktlinien erhöht FineNailsLondon das Maniküre-Erlebnis für zu Hause.
          Wir glauben daran, dass unseren Kunden unabhängig davon, wer sie sind und was sie tun, eine perfekte, langanhaltende Maniküre hilft, Ihre Persönlichkeit zum Ausdruck zu bringen.
          Unsere Produkte bieten dabei genau das, was es braucht: langanhaltende Ergebnisse, sehr hohe Deckkraft und vor allem effizientes schnelles Trocknen ohne viel Equipment. FineNailsLondon holt das Nagelstudio nach Hause. Spart Zeit, Geld und Nerven.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SECOND ABOUT US SECTION -->
    <div class="about-Fine row">
      <div class="about-Fine-text col-11 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
        <h2>About Josefine</h2>
        <p>
          Josefine Musche is the founder of LondonFineNails. She named the company after her favourite city and nickname, which her mother gave her, who taught her how <strong>important it is to have beautiful, clean nails and to be independent and brave</strong>.
          Before founding her LondonFineNails brand in August 2020, she worked for 3 years as a strategic buyer and product developer in e-commerce in Berlin. But the quality of life has moved her life centre to London. When she arrived, she realised that London had everything she wanted except the perfect nail polish. When she saw the opportunity to create an exceptionally long-lasting nail polish where customers could get expert nail care at home, reliably and in a time-saving manner, and enjoy their precious time for more valuable things than a visit to the nail studio, she founded LondonFineNails.
          Fine lives in London with her boyfriend Moritz, who was also an important reason for moving to London.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-Fine-image col-10 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
        <%= image_tag("nails_pink.jpg") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
